---
title: Claim Run State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> INGESTED : POST /claims\naccepted by API

    INGESTED --> ANALYZING : check_worthy_score >= 0.4\ningestion + detection + entity\nextraction complete

    INGESTED --> CANCELLED : check_worthy_score < 0.4\nclaim not check-worthy

    ANALYZING --> ANALYZING : one or more agents\nstill pending terminal status\n(F or X)

    ANALYZING --> SYNTHESIZED : all 10 agents published\nSTOP messages\nAND synthesizer emitted\nVERDICT F-status

    SYNTHESIZED --> PUBLISHED : Consumer API read observations\nvalidated schema\npersisted verdict

    SYNTHESIZED --> SYNTHESIZED : schema validation failed —\nawaiting investigation

    PUBLISHED --> [*] : terminal state\naudit log retained

    CANCELLED --> [*] : terminal state\naudit log retained

    note right of INGESTED
        status = "INGESTED"
        Run record created.
        Ingestion agent dispatched.
    end note

    note right of ANALYZING
        status = "ANALYZING"
        Orchestrator monitors completion register.
        Parallel fan-out active during this state.
        completed_agent_count increments per STOP.
    end note

    note right of SYNTHESIZED
        status = "SYNTHESIZED"
        All observations written to Redis Streams.
        Verdict publication in progress.
    end note

    note right of PUBLISHED
        status = "PUBLISHED"
        JSON verdict available via Consumer API.
        Observation streams retained in Redis.
    end note

    note right of CANCELLED
        status = "CANCELLED"
        Reason recorded in observations.
        No agents dispatched beyond
        claim-detector.
    end note
